OL,6,FCCTV footage captured the moment
OL,7,FRichard Kelly crashed into Darlington
OL,8,FHippodrome Credit: Durham Constabulary
OL,10,FA man has been jailed after
OL,11,Fdeliberately driving his car into a
OL,12,Ftheatre at high speed.
OL,14,FRichard Kelly crashed the Ford Puma
OL,15,Finto Darlington Hippodrome at around
OL,16,F3.40pm on Thursday 7 March.
