OL,3,CFootage captures man deliberately
OL,4,Cdriving car into theatre
OL,6,FThe 47-year-old drove down Park Place
OL,7,Fand straight through a junction before
OL,8,Fsmashing through the metal barriers
OL,9,Foutside the theatre and into the front
OL,10,Fof the building.
OL,12,FThe incident was captured on CCTV and
OL,13,Fshowed his car narrowly missing other
OL,14,Fvehicles and pedestrians as it
OL,15,Fcareered across Parkgate.
OL,17,FKelly had not been wearing a seatbelt
OL,18,Fat the time of the crash and had to be
OL,19,Fhelped out of the car by emergency
OL,20,Fservices. He suffered broken ribs and
OL,21,Fwas taken to hospital.
