OL,3,CFootage captures man deliberately
OL,4,Cdriving car into theatre
OL,6,FHe smelled strongly of alcohol after
OL,7,Fthe incident and was later arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of dangerous driving and
OL,9,Fcharged with the offence.
OL,11,FKelly, of Bourne Court, Darlington,
OL,12,Fadmitted the charge, claiming he
OL,13,Fdeliberately drove at the building
OL,14,Fafter pressing the accelerator instead
OL,15,Fof the brake.
OL,17,FAppearing at Teesside Crown Court on
OL,18,FWednesday 1 May, Kelly was sentenced
OL,19,Fto 12 months in prison and was banned
OL,20,Ffrom driving for 16 months.
