OL,6,FDetective Inspector David Bailey, of
OL,7,FDurham Constabulary, said: "Kelly's
OL,8,Fbehaviour that day was utterly
OL,9,Freckless ` he drove at excessive
OL,10,Fspeeds and straight across a busy
OL,11,Fjunction without any thought for other
OL,12,Froad users or pedestrians.
OL,14,F"It is only by sheer luck that nobody
OL,15,Felse was injured as a result of his
OL,16,Factions.
