OL,6,F"If he had chosen to commit this
OL,7,Foffence only moments before, several
OL,8,Fpeople would have been seriously
OL,9,Finjured or even killed as a result of
OL,10,Fhis actions.
OL,12,F"I am pleased he has admitted his
OL,13,Fguilt and can reflect on the
OL,14,Fconsequences of his careless behaviour
OL,15,Fwhile he is behind bars."
